longBusinessSummary: Ishan Dyes and Chemicals Limited manufactures, trades in, exports, imports, and deals chemicals used in dyes and pigment in India. The company offers copper phthalocyanine blue crude, solvent dye, and pigment alpha and beta blues. Ishan Dyes and Chemicals Limited was incorporated in 1993 and is based in Ahmedabad, India.
